text: Radio Caroline is a British radio station founded in 1964 by Ronan O'Rahilly. It may also refer to: *Radio Caroline (Netherlands), a Dutch station styled after Radio Caroline, and later changed its name to Radio Waddenzee *Radio Caroline (New Zealand), an earlier radio station in Timaru, New Zealand *Radio Caroline International, name adopted of the earlier Radio North Sea International *Radio Caroline Volume 1, the second DJ mix album by Miss Kittin
title: Radio Caroline (disambiguation)
